Street Scenes--Manhattan: A sleeping derelict in the municipal square to the rear of the County Court House at Foley Square. To the right is Worth Street.

1938-9

Alexander Alland

This photo is one of a series that appeared in the published volume "Portrait of N. Y." by Felix Reisenberg and Alex. Alland, IRGV.
title: Street scenes - Sleeping derelict.
